<span id="freeTextContainer2880717030743609336">I don&apos;t know what it was but I thought this book was so boring. It felt like someone had gone on an interesting trip and tried to to put everything they saw and learned down on paper, throw in a couple of characters and call it a novel. I thought none of the characters were compelling and I&apos;m shocked I actually finished it, even if it was mostly skimming the last 150 pages.<br/><br/>I have to say it&apos;s refreshing to really dislike something every once in awhile.</span>
  <span id="freeText2880717030743609336" style="display:none">I don't know what it was but I thought this book was so boring. It felt like someone had gone on an interesting trip and tried to to put everything they saw and learned down on paper, throw in a couple of characters and call it a novel. I thought none of the characters were compelling and I'm shocked I actually finished it, even if it was mostly skimming the last 150 pages.<br /><br />I have to say it's refreshing to really dislike something every once in awhile.</span>
